.TH wxRadioBox 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxRadioBox \- A radio box item is used to select one of number of mutually exclusive choices.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
It is displayed as a vertical column or horizontal row of labelled buttons.

